<br type="automatic_original" />
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">１図（コスミ）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　黒１のコスミが白の眼を取る急所でした。</sentence>
<sentence>白２に黒３とハネ、白４以下６のあと、黒７のツギ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<sentence type="quasi">１図</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</caption>
</figureBlock>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">２図（続）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　白８と切ってきても黒９とハネれば、三手対四手で黒が攻め合い勝ちです。</sentence>
<sentence>また、黒ａでも良し。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
